text: Wesley Koolhof and Matwé Middelkoop were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Íñigo Cervantes and Oriol Roca Batalla won the title after Ariel Behar and Enrique López-Pérez retired while trailing 2–6, 5–6. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Category:Copa Sevilla doubles Copa Sevilla - Doubles
